board.description: MIMXRT1050-EVK: EVK Development Platform for i.MX MIMXRT1052 and MIMXRT1051 MCUs

specific.content: The NXP MIMXRT1050-EVK is a development board for the i.MX MIMXRT1052 and MIMXRT1051 600 MHz 32-bit ARM® Cortex®-M7 MCUs

board.name: EVK-MIMXRT1050-AGM01
board.description: Sensor Toolbox Development Platform for FXAS21002C and FXOS8700C 9-Axis Solution

specific.content:
Demonstration Custom Kit (FRDM-STBC-AGM01 Sensor Shield Development Board with EVK-MIMXRT1050 Board):
  • Enables quick and easy visualization of 9-Axis (3 Axis Gyroscope + 6-Axis E-compass) sensor data and results.

board.name: EVK-MIMXRT1050-OM13588
board.description: USB Type-C Shield Board for Kinetis Freedom Board

specific.content: The USB Type-C shield board combined with a Kinetis Power Delivery SDK allows a system designer to tether a USB Type-C connector to any Kinetis development platform.
